      • getCommissionAmount

        MonetaryAmount getCommissionAmount()
        Gets the commission amount for this transaction. This is equal to the transaction amount, for transaction types that send money to the producer; it is equal to the negation of the transaction amount, for transaction types that receive money from the producer.
